headline: Want to Invest in Quantum Computing? 3 Stocks That Are Great Buys Right Now.
summary: Quantum computing could be the next frontier for computers and cloud-based services.  While traditional computers still store data in binary bits of zeros and ones, quantum computers store zeros and ones simultaneously in qubits.  If you want to profit from that secular trend, you should consider buying these three stocks: IonQ (NYSE: IONQ), D-Wave Quantum (NYSE: QBTS), and IBM (NYSE: IBM).
